title: Europe and US Country Size Comparison Map - How...
text:
FREE Newsletter. Sign Up Now! Know what it takes to drive around your state? Then see how your state matches up with Western European countries with our interactive map 
The map of the United States sits on top of our map of Western Europe. To move the map, click on the red dot (or any line on the US map). Your mouse will "grab" the dot and you'll be able to move the US map around to align it over Europe. (IE and Opera users may have to click the map once to get it to start working).
